Look, it's Mark.

06:14.749 --> 06:15.867
What are you doing?

06:15.992 --> 06:18.856
What? I'm just checking
to make sure this lens works.

06:18.981 --> 06:19.878
Good.

06:26.282 --> 06:27.471
Are you ready?

06:27.596 --> 06:30.050
Oh, no, I need another hour
to get ready.

06:30.217 --> 06:32.684
Seriously? 'Cause I think
the movie starts in like...

06:34.477 --> 06:35.894
You're joking around right now.

06:36.997 --> 06:38.418
This is gonna be fun.

06:38.586 --> 06:40.514
You know, with a body like this,

06:40.639 --> 06:42.589
you don't get the brains too.

06:43.012 --> 06:44.688
That was silly.

06:46.775 --> 06:48.032
Are they dating now?

06:48.200 --> 06:49.571
Brendanawicz is the man.

