to have somebody to talk to.

10:43.080 --> 10:44.309
Man, oh, man.

10:44.477 --> 10:46.061
So how's Ann?
She's doing good?

10:46.249 --> 10:48.700
I miss her so much, it's ridiculous.

10:48.825 --> 10:51.775
- How's she doing?
- Doing good tonight. She's out on a...

10:51.943 --> 10:53.386
Ann is great.

10:54.269 --> 10:55.821
And I bet she really misses you.

10:57.240 --> 10:59.157
I'm gonna need more
if I'm gonna stay up.

10:59.325 --> 11:01.380
- Is that candy?
- It's a necklace made out of candy.

11:01.505 --> 11:03.579
- Want one?
