16:56.352 --> 16:58.152
Should I get you home right now?

16:58.277 --> 17:00.977
You two go ahead.
I'm gonna stay here and wait for Tom.

17:01.398 --> 17:03.206
- Are you sure?
- Yeah.

17:03.331 --> 17:04.881
Prison changes a man.

17:05.383 --> 17:08.276
I think he'll wanna see a familiar face
when he gets back on the outside.

17:09.009 --> 17:11.369
Well, OK, then.
See you, Leslie.

17:18.537 --> 17:20.872
Yo. I had to wait
till my dad fell asleep

17:21.040 --> 17:22.839
so I could steal his keys.

17:23.117 --> 17:24.125
You ready?

17:24.609 --> 17:26.019
