17:44.977 --> 17:47.227
Terrible things happened last time.

17:49.026 --> 17:50.676
So I guess I'll just...

17:51.685 --> 17:53.035
see you tomorrow.

17:55.754 --> 17:56.554
Bye.

17:59.893 --> 18:01.493
