and he is in his home.

19:12.235 --> 19:14.897
Just important that they're both
in their homes.

19:15.022 --> 19:16.237
Mark's an idiot.

19:16.614 --> 19:19.616
You could do a lot better than him.
Forget about him.

19:20.888 --> 19:21.988
Thanks, Tom.

19:23.425 --> 19:26.206
