19:33.576 --> 19:36.818
You don't think I know the difference
between carrots and marijuana?

19:39.245 --> 19:41.504
Is that the house there
where your best friend lives?

19:41.629 --> 19:43.172
Where she saw the van from?

19:45.347 --> 19:46.267
I get it.

19:46.435 --> 19:47.236
What?

19:47.468 --> 19:49.229
You wanted to check up
on your friend

19:49.397 --> 19:51.022
and that guy, your ex,

19:51.461 --> 19:55.026
